{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "a5391dc6-0400-40c2-9b51-9558d84ae393", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a5391dc6-0400-40c2-9b51-9558d84ae393@1.pkg/1772597522909/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597523285", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a5391dc6-0400-40c2-9b51-9558d84ae393@1.pkg/1772597522909/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597523285"}, "identifier": "a5391dc6-0400-40c2-9b51-9558d84ae393", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>C:材料中，国务院提出要“高效办成一件事”，建设服务型政府，这是因为政府权力来源于人民;政府的宗旨是为人民服务，为人民谋利益，故C说法正确；</p>\n\n<p>AB:这是政府工作的要求，不是国务院提出要“高效办成一件事”的原因，故AB不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>D:材料没有体现出政务公开、科学民主决策的内容，故D不符合题意;</p>\n\n<p>故本题选C。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2024山东菏泽中考真题）&nbsp;国务院提出要把“高效办成一件事”作为优化政务服务、提升行政效能的重要抓手。比如，借助数字技术等手段，推进线下办事“只进一门”、线上办事“一网通办”、群众诉求“一线应答”，优化办事流程。这是因为（&nbsp; &nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2024山东菏泽中考真题） 国务院提出要把“高效办成一件事”作为优化政务服务、提升行政效能的重要抓手。比如，借助数字技术等手段，推进线下办事“只进一门”、线上办事“一网通办”、群众诉求“一线应答”，优化办事流程。这是因为（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a5391dc6-0400-40c2-9b51-9558d84ae393@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754818487791", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>依法行政是法治政府行使权力的基本准则 &nbsp;</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>政府的各项权力都应该在法治轨道上运行</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>政府的宗旨是为人民服务，为人民谋利益</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>推进政务公开能够促进政府科学民主决策</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编·2024山东菏泽中考真题）&nbsp;国务院提出要把“高效办成一件事”作为优化政务服务、提升行政效能的重要抓手。比如，借助数字技术等手段，推进线下办事“只进一门”、线上办事“一网通办”、群众诉求“一线应答”，优化办事流程。这是因为（&nbsp; &nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "a5391dc6-0400-40c2-9b51-9558d84ae393", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "（改编·2024山东菏泽中考真题） 国务院提出要把“高效办成一件事”作为优化政务服务、提升行政效能的重要抓手。比如，借助数字技术等手段，推进线下办事“只进一门”、线上办事“一网通办”、群众诉求“一线应答”，优化办事流程。这是因为（   ）"}, "global_descrip